VICTORIA, Seychelles, July 13, 2022/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            President Wavel Ramkalawan chaired a scheduled meeting of the Cabinet today, Wednesday 13th July at which a number of policy and legal memoranda were considered.


                                Cabinet approved the Mayor of Victoria Bill, 2022 which will guide the elections of the Mayor of Victoria
                            

Cabinet approved the Mayor of Victoria Bill, 2022 which will guide the elections of the Mayor of Victoria.

Cabinet approved a proposal to dissolve the Agency for National Human Resource Development. A new Division will be created within the Ministry of Education to oversee the scholarship administration related functions while the Employment Department will take over the Human Resource planning and development functions.

Further details to the media will be provided by the relevant Ministry.